Project Scoop
Topic: Infrastructure, Data Center
Company: Nike, Inc., Beaverton, OR
Opportunity: A front line source has indicated that data center infrastructure management is a spending priority. The organization has selected internal tools and is currently implementing. This initiative will take place at the company headquarters. The organization uses contingent/contract workers for technology initiatives. (Live on 1/16/2017)
Update: We have created new tools in house for our data center infrastructure management.







